# Sequencer Project Rules

## Hardware Configuration
- Target device: ESP32-C6 from XIAO
- Language: MicroPython
- Display: 6x20 neopixel display on pin d0 (configurable)
- Display origin: Bottom-left corner (0,0)
- Display matrix: 20 columns (x-axis), 6 rows (y-axis)
- Gate pixels: 6 additional pixels (120-125) for gate control

## Development Guidelines
- Always ask before making changes to code
- Provide GitHub commit message for each change
- Make small changes for microcommits
- Inline comments are acceptable
- Each file must have a header describing contents and algorithm
- Use neopixel brightness at 10% by default

## Display Coordinate System
- Position (0,0) = pixel 0
- Position (0,1) = pixel 1  
- Position (1,0) = pixel 6
- Position (1,1) = pixel 7
- Position (19,5) = pixel 119
- Gate pixels: 120-125 (gate1-gate6)

## Color Palette
Red, Green, Blue, White, Cyan, Magenta, Purple, Grey, Yellow, Orange, Indigo, Violet

## Gate Control
- Red = gate off (0)
- Green = gate on (1)
